            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I think I'd somehow convinced myself that the format argument is optional which looks like it's not right.\n\nThat looks fairly easily fixed: we just change\n\nhttps://github.com/cython/cython/blob/74357c36df5d28bae1ecd1eb45bdcafe1f80426a/Cython/Utility/CythonFunction.c#L650\n\nto pass an argument (probably `1` for `annotatelib.VALUE`). I wonder if it's worth trying other formats if that fails though in the hope of maximizing the chance of working \n\nI'll try to add a quite test for the \"wrapping cyfuncs with non-cyfuncs\" and \"wrapping non-cyfuncs with cyfuncs\" cases.\n\nThanks for the report.",
